NuxBank
========

An item bank plugin, using spout to make great GUI.


Installation
------------

* Download the latest jar [here](https://github.com/NuxosMinecraft/NuxBank/downloads).
* Copy the downloaded jar file into the plugins folder and rename it to "NuxStats.jar".

Permissions' nodes
------------------

* nuxbank.build - Allow to build a bank sign.
* nuxbank.c2b - Allow to transfer to the bank the content of a chest.

Commands
--------

* /c2b - Transfers to the bank the content of a chest